casebody.data:
MORRIS PLAINS HOLDING VF, LLC, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
MILANO FRENCH CLEANERS, INC. and Alfonso Meghnagi, Defendants,
and
Vito Meghnagi, Defendant-Petitioner. C-41 September Term 2018
081228 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000604-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
